				while it is possible for you to equip multiple types of weapons you usually only start out with one weapon skill type (ie rogues start with dagger skill), but you can go to major cities and train in other weapons that are allowed to be used by your class (ie as a rogue i went to the warrior quarter in undercity and trained in swords).  you just need the training to equip them dude.<br />
