			<tr><td colspan="2">
				<div class="postbody">
				Your class determines what weapon skills you can learn, while your race usually determines what you start with. For instance, an Orc Warrior starts with axes, a Tauren starts with maces, and Undead start with swords. You can train mace and 2h maces in Thunder Bluff, axes/2h in Orgrimmar, and swords/2h in Undercity. Don't think there's a level requirement, just need to pay 10s.
<br />

<br />
When you get to the city, talk to a guard and ask for directions to the weapon master. He'll tell you wehre to find 'em and mard it on your map.<br />
				<span class="gensmall"></span><br />
				</div>
			</td></tr>
