This also depends on class, and on the weapon type. For most classes, most weapon types are available at level 1, but in some cases (like polearms for Warriors/Hunters), you can't learn them until later...learning polearms as a hunter takes a trip to Undercity, and spending a gold (!).
<br />

<br />
Here's a listing of all the skills that Priests can train in, and what level they get them:
<br />

